Private Sub Display_AnimationStart()
On Error GoTo ErrHandler
Dim PACOTE_EQP As String
PACOTE_EQP = Text1.Caption PONTEIRO = Mid(PACOTE_EQP, 3, 1)
If PONTEIRO = "-" Then PACOTE_EQP_TIPO = Left(PACOTE_EQP, 2) PACOTE_EQP_NUMERO = Mid(PACOTE_EQP, 4, 8) Else PACOTE_EQP_TIPO = Left(PACOTE_EQP, 3) PACOTE_EQP_NUMERO = Mid(PACOTE_EQP, 5, 8) End If
AlarmEventSummary1.FilterDefinition = " EventSource LIKE '" & PACOTE_EQP_TIPO & "' And EventSource LIKE '" & PACOTE_EQP_NUMERO & "'"
FactoryTalkAlarmandEventLogViewer1.WhereClause = " SourceName LIKE '%" & PACOTE_EQP_TIPO & "%' And SourceName LIKE '%" & PACOTE_EQP_NUMERO & "%'"
Exit Sub ErrHandler:
End Sub
